Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: gecko-controller
Version: 0.7.5
Summary: Raspberry Pi-based temperature, light and UV controller for gecko enclosure
Author: Ian Ross Williams
Author-email: ianrosswilliams@gmail.com
Requires-Python: >=3.9
License-File: LICENSE

Automated temperature and light controller for gecko enclosure with OLED display support. Features include temperature and humidity monitoring, light cycle control, heat management, and OLED status display.
